1.1.0
  Changed: xlibs 1.2.5 dependency.

1.0.9
  Gameplay:
    Changed: default online guard threshold from 70 to 80
  Diagnostics:
    Added: per-operation timing traces (collect, sort, per-release) when debug_log enabled
  Compatibility:
    Added: task target squad protection (assault, bounty, hostage, delivery squads never released)
    Fixed: task target squad check running on monsters (wasted luabind calls)
    Fixed: delete_common_squads removing bounty/hostage quest targets
  MCM:
    Added: version displayed at startup (mod + xlibs)
    Changed: MCM visual refresh
    Fixed: Russian MCM encoding restored (windows-1251)
  X-Ray & xlibs:
    Added: xsquad.is_task_target for O(1) task squad detection (replaces per-entity bounty scan)
    Added: log deadbanding reduces repeated lines in busy areas
    Fixed: release_squads crash on stale SIMBOARD IDs after repopulate
    Fixed: find_online_squads no longer re-evaluates rejected squads
  Performance:
    Changed: entity removal spread across frames via xslice (zero stutter, 0.05ms average per release)

